          <p><%= image_tag "faq/jerry.jpg", :alt => "Jerry", :class => "profile-pic pull-left" %> Currently the president of DevCon, Jerry is also president and CEO of the homegrown award-winning software development company <a href="http://exist.com" target="_blank">Exist</a>. Just like Winston, Jerry is an avid supporter of propelling the growth of ICT industry in the Philippines, particularly in Cebu. He has chaired the Cebu ICT &amp; BPO in 2009 and 2010 and has co-chaired the Philippine Open Source Summit held in Cebu in 2008. He is also VP of the Cebu Educational Development Foundation for Information Technology (CEDF-IT), a consortium dedicated to workforce development initiatives in the ICT and IT-enabled services industries.</p>
